<milestone n="1" unit="juan"/>
<pb n="0232a" xml:id="I01.0087.0232a" ed="I"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0232a01"/><cb:docNumber>No. 87</cb:docNumber>
<lb ed="I" n="0232a02"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"></cb:mulu><cb:jhead><title>棲閑寺邑義六十人造像記</title></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<pb n="0233a" xml:id="I01.0087.0233a" ed="I"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0233a01"/><p cb:type="pre" xml:id="pI01p0233a0101">夫理寂虛凝。非浮情所側。假形名相。會趣消氓。邑義□□□□□□□□
<lb ed="I" n="0233a02"/>十人等。萇悲二<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0233001" n="0233001"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0233001" n="0233001"/><anchor xml:id="beg0233001" n="0233001"/>鼠<anchor xml:id="end0233001"/>交侵。形從電逝。夙霄涕慕。仰戀真容。心同歸□□□□
<lb ed="I" n="0233a03"/>寶。遂割湌糊口。捨服履寒。共在棲閑寺敬造石碑像一軀。上為皇<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">帝</unclear>□□。
<lb ed="I" n="0233a04"/>下及三塗。其像也。石勝京山。匠巧般倕。相<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">脫</unclear>真儀。妙過世有。聞之者。望風
<lb ed="I" n="0233a05"/>如迴首。<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0233002" n="0233002"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0233002" n="0233002"/><anchor xml:id="beg0233002" n="0233002"/>睹<anchor xml:id="end0233002"/>之者。肅敬如踟躕。其地土號瑯琊。帝室遺居。前距高崗。卻背金
<lb ed="I" n="0233a06"/>墉。左帶萇沂。右<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">俠</unclear>山峰。寺則林同玄菀。下若遊仙。端<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0233003" n="0233003"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0233003" n="0233003"/><anchor xml:id="beg0233003" n="0233003"/>坐<anchor xml:id="end0233003"/>獨念。叡智通神。邑
<lb ed="I" n="0233a07"/>義等。並識<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">達</unclear>玄宗。妙<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0233004" n="0233004"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0233004" n="0233004"/><anchor xml:id="beg0233004" n="0233004"/>體<anchor xml:id="end0233004"/>空寂。敦崇三寶。於茲日益。其辭曰。
<lb ed="I" n="0233a08"/>微微能絕。顯著滿空。含生等潤。不言如功。
<lb ed="I" n="0233a09"/>慕仰雙林。圖鏤真容。<anchor xml:id="beg_1" type="star"/>睹<anchor xml:id="end_1"/>茲妙相。夙夜乾恭。
<lb ed="I" n="0233a10"/>陰陽迭<anchor xml:id="nkr_note_orig_0233005" n="0233005"/><anchor xml:id="nkr_note_mod_0233005" n="0233005"/><anchor xml:id="beg0233005" n="0233005"/>布<anchor xml:id="end0233005"/>。物故虧盈。悲同彫落。刊石留名。　　司州汲　郡尚孝舉之<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">辭</unclear>□。
<lb ed="I" n="0233a11"/><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">大</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">齊</unclear>天統五年歲次己丑九月丁亥朔十四□□卯。邑義六十人等之碑頌。</p></cb:div>
